The paper deals with image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves contour extraction and optimization, which are also relevant to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM). The method utilizes prior information about the shape of the objects, which suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
